{"word":"φωνέω","slug":"φωνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>φωνέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φωνή\">φωνή</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘utter a sound designed to attract attention’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of a rooster <b>crow <a href='B:470 26:34'>Mt 26:34</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of a human <b>cry out, proclaim with emphasis <a href='B:480 1:26'>Mk 1:26</a>; <a href='B:490 8:8'>Lk 8:8</a>, <a href='B:490 8:54'>54</a>; <a href='B:490 23:46'>23:46</a>; <a href='B:510 16:28'>Ac 16:28</a>; <a href='B:730 14:18'>Rv 14:18</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘call to oneself’, <b>summon, call for <a href='B:470 27:47'>Mt 27:47</a>; <a href='B:480 9:35'>Mk 9:35</a>; <a href='B:480 10:49'>10:49</a>; <a href='B:490 19:15'>Lk 19:15</a>; <a href='B:500 1:48'>J 1:48</a>; <a href='B:500 2:9'>2:9</a>; <a href='B:500 11:28'>11:28</a>; <a href='B:500 12:17'>12:17</a>; <a href='B:500 18:33'>18:33</a>; <a href='B:510 10:18'>Ac 10:18</a>; invite <a href='B:490 14:12'>Lk 14:12</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> identify in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> address, <b>call <a href='B:500 10:3'>J 10:3</a>; <a href='B:500 13:13'>13:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:φωλεός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:φωνή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}